high_descs: Turn to the right and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Step to the left and face the cabinet below the microwave.
Place the apple in the bowl in the cabinet under the microwave.
Pick up the bowl with the tomato in it from in the cabinet under the microwave.
Look up to face the microwave on the counter.
Place the bowl with a tomato in it in the microwave and close it.
Turn around and walk across the room and turn right to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the knife on the kitchen table.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Cut the tomato in the microwave into slices.
anns.task_desc: To place a tomato in a bowl in the microwave as well as cut the tomato into slices.

high_descs: Turn right to go to the counter on the left of the stove.
Pick up the bigger tomato on the right.
Move left to the end of the counter.
Place the tomato in bowl in the cabinet under the counter.
Pick up the bowl with tomato in it
Bring up the bowl to the microwave.
Place the bowl with tomato inside the microwave.
Turn around and go to the round table.
Pick up the gray knife between the hand soap and bread.
Turn right and go back to the microwave.
Slice the tomato in the bowl inside the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Slice the tomato in a bowl in the microwave

high_descs: Turn right, walk forward, turn left and walk to the edge of the kitchen counter.
Pick up the big tomato on the top right of the counter.
Turn left, step forward, and turn right to face the microwave.
Open the bottom cabinet door under the microwave to reveal a bowl.
Place the tomato into the bowl already the cabinet, close the cabinet door.
Stand up to face the microwave.
Open microwave door, place the bowl inside next to the egg, close the door.
Turn right, walk forward, then turn right and walk to the kitchen table.
Pick up the knife to the left of the bread.
Turn right and walk back to the microwave.
Open the microwave on the counter, push the tomato, close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place tomato in bowl, put in microwave and tap with knife.
